                <head>No. 793.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Fish</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Beardsley</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1874-01-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 24, 1874</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Bill to authorize acceptance of the judicial reform is before Congress. You will
                    be informed when that body acts.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FISH.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
